	<td class="alt2" width="175" align="center" valign="top" nowrap="nowrap"><b>BattleAxe</b>
<span class="smallfont">
	<br />
	Mystic<br />
		
	
	<br />
	Joined: Apr 2001<br />
	Location: Louisiana
</span></td>
	
	<td class="alt2" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p>There are several game bugs running around that become really significant due to the number of people in the bazaar, and the ability of certain spells to knock people offline.<br />
When setting up your trader for the night, do the following:<br />
Minimize clip plane, set opacity to 0%, /showspelleffects off<br />
face a wall or look at the floor<br />
turn off all chat - ooc, shout, auction, guild, all chat channels<br />
set all spells to yourself or group<br />
make sure badword filter is off (/filter badword)<br />
<br />
These settings get my trader through the night more often.</p>
	
	
	
		<div>__________________<br />"Shammies heal like a lvl 24 Druid with Epilepsy" - The Quon</div>
	
	
