	<td class="alt1" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p>I believe the crashing to desk top is related to bad item links due to the <b>Bad Word</b> filter.  If you turn that filter off by typing <i><b>"/Filter Badword"</i></b>  This has sure help my trader stay up though the night.  I also try to stay away from setting up too near the banks as those places seem to be a favorite place for people to set up and just are lag central.  Lord for bid a bard desides to sing though the night near there with a annoying AoE song.  Hehehe good luck all you traders.</p>
	
	
	
	
	
