	<td class="alt2" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p>I can confirm the badword filter issue.  I run a 24/7 trader that was unable to stay on for the night after LoY came out, with the typical crashed to the desktop.  Since I removed the badword filter (it got switched on as default with the strart of LoY) I got 5 day sessions without drop.  From what I gathered it was an issue with the badword filter colliding with linked items - and in the bazaar someone is always linking items, only a matter of time till it gets one that crashes you.</p>
	
	
	
