	<td class="alt1" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p>Believe it.  You know when your lag meter goes all staticky and yellow/red?  That is a problem with the game code, not your connection.  And oddly enough, pinging your local machine DOES work.<br />
<br />
I 2box on the same computer and the minute I open up that second window both lag meters do the staticky thing.  I made a small batch file after reading about this fix on the official EQ website tech boards, and it fixed the problem.<br />
<br />
My batch file looks like this:<br />
<br />
:LOOP<br />
ping 127.0.0.1<br />
goto LOOP<br />
<br />
It is named sonysucks.bat heheheh</p>
	
	
	
